<text><body>
<lb n="0225b22"/>
<milestone unit="juan" n="1"/>
<lb n="0225b23"/>
<lb n="0225b24"/><head type="no">No. 1248</head><div1 type="dharani">
<lb n="0225b25"/><juan fun="open" n="001"><mulu type="卷" n="001"/><jhead><note n="0225002" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">【原】享和元年刊長谷寺藏本，【甲】高山寺藏古寫本</note>北方毘沙門天王隨軍護法真言</jhead></juan>
<lb n="0225b26"/>
<lb n="0225b27"/><byline type="Translator">特進試鴻臚卿大興善寺三藏沙門
<lb n="0225b28"/>大廣智不空別行翻譯不入正經</byline>
<lb n="0225b29"/><p type="dharani"><note n="0225003" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">此梵字真言附載於卷末</note>曩謨囉多曩<note place="inline">二合</note>多羅<note place="inline">二合</note><note n="0225004" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔多〕－&M062485;【原】</note><sic n="0225004" corr="＆lac；" resp="【原】">多</sic>夜耶阿馱佉路
<pb ed="T" id="T21.1248.0225c" n="0225c"/>
<lb n="0225c01"/>步多囉<note place="inline">二合</note>耶地舍耶<note place="inline">二</note>吠室囉<note place="inline">二合</note>摩拏野<note place="inline">三</note>
<lb n="0225c02"/>摩賀囉惹野<note place="inline">四</note>藥迦灑<note place="inline">二合</note>地婆多婆<note place="inline">五上</note>娑都
<lb n="0225c03"/>哆娑娑室囉跛囉<note place="inline">二合</note>娑賀娜耶呬<note place="inline">賢二反</note>摩馱吒
<lb n="0225c04"/>吒<note place="inline">去<note n="0225005" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">呼＝乎【甲】</note><app n="0225005"><lem>呼</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">乎</rdg></app></note>尾跛囉<note place="inline">二合</note>灑夜迷跛娜也<note place="inline">二合</note>他<note n="0225006" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">保＝俁【甲】＊</note><app n="0225006"><lem>保</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">俁</rdg></app>
<lb n="0225c05"/>&CB04048;&CB00135;<app type="＊" source="0225006"><lem>保</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">俁</rdg></app>&CB04048;&CB00135;俱沙吠室羅摩拏野摩賀囉惹
<lb n="0225c06"/>耶綺<note place="inline">佉罽反</note>婆<note place="inline">去</note>馱伽&CB00135;多囉摩熾都麼麼<note place="inline">某甲受持</note>捺
<lb n="0225c07"/>娑<note place="inline">上</note>娑馱耶娑那謨婆&CB00344;&CB00085;帝悉殿都麼多囉
<lb n="0225c08"/>跛馱&CB00135;娑婆<note place="inline">二合</note>賀</p>
<lb n="0225c09"/><p>若行者受持此&CB00057;者。先須畫像。於彩色中並
<lb n="0225c10"/>不得和膠。於白&CB00626;上畫一毘沙門神。七寶莊
<lb n="0225c11"/>嚴衣甲。左手執戟&CB00266;。右手<note n="0225007" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">托＝託【甲】</note><app n="0225007"><lem>托</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">託</rdg></app>腰上。其神&CB00560;
<lb n="0225c12"/>下作二夜叉鬼。身並作黑色。其毘沙門面。作
<lb n="0225c13"/>甚可畏形惡眼視一切鬼神勢。其塔奉釋迦
<lb n="0225c14"/>牟尼佛。教汝若領天兵守界擁護國土。何護
<lb n="0225c15"/>吾法。即擁遣第三子那吒捧行莫離其側。汝
<lb n="0225c16"/>眼毒惡恐損眾生。爾時行者。若誦此&CB00057;時。就
<lb n="0225c17"/>好地。勿使有穢惡之處。極令淨潔取牛糞塗
<lb n="0225c18"/>地。即以香泥塗之。散種種花燒香供養。行者
<lb n="0225c19"/>上下衣服。並須清淨一上廁一洗浴。白月十
<lb n="0225c20"/>五日夜。起首對像前。誦&CB00057;滿十萬遍訖。然
<lb n="0225c21"/>後更取香泥復塗壇上。更取上妙好花散壇
<lb n="0225c22"/>中。設種種飲食。行者取薰陸香一百八顆。各
<lb n="0225c23"/>&CB00057;一遍散著火中。爾時毘沙門即現其身。行
<lb n="0225c24"/>者若見神時取上好食飲。供養毘沙門神通。
<lb n="0225c25"/>行者心中所願其神悉見。若行者不見神時。
<lb n="0225c26"/>即虛空中有聲<note n="0225008" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">云＝告言&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0225008"><lem>云</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">告言</rdg></app>。汝但<note n="0225009" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">存＝懃&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0225009"><lem>存</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">懃</rdg></app>心<note n="0225010" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">持誦＝誦&CB00057;&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0225010"><lem>持誦</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">誦&CB00057;</rdg></app>。一切
<lb n="0225c27"/>事汝欲者悉如意。若不見神及不聞聲。但有
<lb n="0225c28"/>大風。或雲遍滿布其壇上。其法即成就。若
<lb n="0225c29"/>無上件等相。<note n="0225011" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">行者＝更&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0225011"><lem>行者</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">更</rdg></app>誦&CB00057;<note n="0225012" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（一）&M062403;＋七【原】</note><app n="0225012"><lem>七</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">一七</rdg></app>遍。縛得<note n="0225013" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">入＝人&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0225013"><lem>入</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">人</rdg></app>者
<pb ed="T" id="T21.1248.0226a" n="0226a"/>
<lb n="0226a01"/>其法即成。更勿懷疑</p><p place="inline">又法若行者欲得喝
<lb n="0226a02"/>囉闍愛敬者。取赤小豆一顆&CB00057;一遍。投火中
<lb n="0226a03"/>燒。如是滿一百八遍。其喝囉闍即遣人<note n="0226001" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">喚來極忽＝喚&CB00057;師如箭急急來&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0226001"><lem>喚
<lb n="0226a04"/>來極忽</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">喚&CB00057;師如箭急急來</rdg></app></p><p place="inline">又法若欲得大<note n="0226002" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">官＝印【甲】</note><app n="0226002"><lem>官</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">印</rdg></app>人愛敬者。取
<lb n="0226a05"/><note n="0226003" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔白〕－【甲】</note><app n="0226003"><lem>白</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>芥子一顆。一&CB00057;投火中燒滿一百八遍。其
<lb n="0226a06"/>官即自<note n="0226004" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔來〕－【甲】</note><app n="0226004"><lem>來</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>敬仰大喜</p><p place="inline">又法於白月十五日
<lb n="0226a07"/>作壇。於像前作八肘。牛糞塗地了。取香泥
<lb n="0226a08"/>重塗了。以五色畫作三重院。其壇內於中畫
<lb n="0226a09"/>一<note n="0226005" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">大＝火&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0226005"><lem>大</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">火</rdg></app>輪。四角拔折羅十字安之。第二院內。
<lb n="0226a10"/>東面畫作一火珠光焰<note n="0226006" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">火＝上&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0226006"><lem>火</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">上</rdg></app>出。南面畫三<note n="0226007" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">股＝鈷【甲】</note><app n="0226007"><lem>股</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">鈷</rdg></app>。
<lb n="0226a11"/>又西面畫一龍口中<note n="0226008" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">並＝著&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0226008"><lem>並</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">著</rdg></app>出蓮華。北面畫一大
<lb n="0226a12"/><note n="0226009" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">縲＝螺&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0226009"><lem>縲</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">螺</rdg></app>。第三院中東面<note n="0226010" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔更〕&M062403;－【原】</note><app n="0226010"><lem>更</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">&lac;</rdg></app>畫師子。南面畫龍
<lb n="0226a13"/>王。西面畫孔雀王<note n="0226011" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔鳥〕&M062403;－【原】</note><app n="0226011"><lem>鳥</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">&lac;</rdg></app>。北面畫<note n="0226012" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">羅剎手＝夜叉王&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0226012"><lem>羅剎手</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">夜叉王</rdg></app>拄<note n="0226013" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">棒＝杖&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0226013"><lem>棒</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">杖</rdg></app>
<lb n="0226a14"/>立地。壇四角各安香水瓶。內著雜&CB00031;楊枝。&CB00057;
<lb n="0226a15"/>師洗浴著新淨衣。於像前設種種飲食供養。
<lb n="0226a16"/>即誦&CB00057;取呵梨勒<note n="0226014" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">一顆＝一百八顆&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0226014"><lem>一顆</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">一百八顆</rdg></app>。一&CB00057;一遍投火中燒
<lb n="0226a17"/>之。滿一百八遍。從今已後。每日送一<note n="0226015" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">&CB04123;＝送金一鋋&M062403;【原】，鎰&M062485;【原】</note><note n="0226015" resp="CBETA" type="mod">&CB04123;＝送金一鋋&M062403;【原】，＝鎰&M062485;【原】</note><app n="0226015"><lem><sic corr="鎰" resp="【原】">&CB04123;</sic></lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">送金一鋋</rdg></app>金
<lb n="0226a18"/>與&CB00057;師永無乏少。若得此物即須用盡。不得
<lb n="0226a19"/>留著</p><p place="inline">又法&CB00057;蘇蜜及&CB00031;子。一百八遍火中
<lb n="0226a20"/>燒之。一切諸天皆大歡喜擁護&CB00057;師</p><p place="inline">又法
<lb n="0226a21"/>若欲遠行時。&CB00057;穀木<note n="0226016" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">柱＝拄杖&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0226016"><lem>柱</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">拄杖</rdg></app>行一切難處。悉得
<lb n="0226a22"/>無怖。又法若惡人相惱亂者。心中想此&CB00057;
<lb n="0226a23"/>神形。復舉心誦&CB00057;。未滿一遍。其人即不能
<lb n="0226a24"/><note n="0226017" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（行）&M062403;＋動【原】</note><app n="0226017"><lem>動</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">行動</rdg></app></p><p place="inline">若欲好者。心放中相<note n="0226018" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">便＋（云即）【甲】</note><app n="0226018"><lem>便</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">便云即</rdg></app>得解脫</p><p place="inline">又
<lb n="0226a25"/>法若欲令怨家<note n="0226019" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">不同住＝遠相&CB00230;&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0226019"><lem>不同住</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">遠相&CB00230;</rdg></app>者。取苦練<note n="0226020" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">子＝木&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0226020"><lem>子</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">木</rdg></app>一百
<lb n="0226a26"/>八顆。一&CB00057;<note n="0226021" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（一）＋投【甲】</note><app n="0226021"><lem>投</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">一投</rdg></app>火中。其人即自遠去</p><p place="inline">又法
<lb n="0226a27"/>若&CB00057;胡麻一百八遍。散著火中。一切人盡來
<lb n="0226a28"/>供養&CB00057;師</p><p place="inline">又法若&CB00057;白芥子一百八遍散山
<lb n="0226a29"/>中。一切惡獸不能傷人。其<note n="0226022" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">狩＝獸&M062485;【原】</note><sic n="0226022" corr="獸" resp="【原】">狩</sic>見人即自伏
<pb ed="T" id="T21.1248.0226b" n="0226b"/>
<lb n="0226b01"/>地不敢傷害。過去已後方即起去</p><p place="inline">又法若
<lb n="0226b02"/>欲乞雨時。<note n="0226023" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔取〕－【甲】</note><app n="0226023"><lem>取</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>杏<note n="0226024" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">子＋（人）【原】</note><app n="0226024"><lem>子</lem><rdg wit="【原】" resp="Taisho">子人</rdg></app>一百八顆都&CB00057;三七遍。
<lb n="0226b03"/>著有龍水中必得雨下。欲止雨時。取梧桐子
<lb n="0226b04"/>火中燒之即止</p><p place="inline">又法若行者欲乞食。先&CB00057;
<lb n="0226b05"/>&CB00425;一百八遍。隨所<note n="0226025" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">到＝致【甲】</note><app n="0226025"><lem>到</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">致</rdg></app>處。自然而得一切飲
<lb n="0226b06"/>食了。飲<note n="0226026" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔食〕－【甲】</note><app n="0226026"><lem>食</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>殘者當時自化<note n="0226027" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">去＝土【甲】</note><app n="0226027"><lem>去</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">土</rdg></app>。若須飲食時。
<lb n="0226b07"/>至心向&CB00425;<note n="0226028" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔者〕&M062403;－【原】</note><app n="0226028"><lem>者</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">&lac;</rdg></app>誦&CB00057;一遍。其&CB00425;依還如故</p><p place="inline">又
<lb n="0226b08"/>法若欲見功<note n="0226029" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">能＝德【甲】＊</note><app n="0226029"><lem>能</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">德</rdg></app>天者。一日一夜不食。於佛
<lb n="0226b09"/>前燒蘇合香。&CB00057;白花一百八遍。以散<note n="0226030" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">神＝佛&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0226030"><lem>神</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">佛</rdg></app>前。
<lb n="0226b10"/>其功<app type="＊" source="0226029"><lem>能</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">德</rdg></app>天即自現身。隨意所須一切願滿。所
<lb n="0226b11"/>求財寶即得稱意</p><p place="inline">若欲<note n="0226031" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">辟＝避&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0226031"><lem>辟</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">避</rdg></app>除一切鬼神。&CB00057;
<lb n="0226b12"/>白芥子及蘇。&CB00057;一顆一遍。投火中燒之即得</p>
<lb n="0226b13"/><p>若有<note n="0226032" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">官＝惡&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0226032"><lem>官</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">惡</rdg></app>人。於三寶<note n="0226033" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">中＝所&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0226033"><lem>中</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">所</rdg></app>起不善心者。惱亂
<lb n="0226b14"/>佛弟子者。欲令起慈心。須作降伏。&CB00057;手<note n="0226034" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">三＝二&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0226034"><lem>三</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">二</rdg></app>
<lb n="0226b15"/>十一遍。遙打之其人即著疾。欲<note n="0226035" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">好＝改&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0226035"><lem>好</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">改</rdg></app>者慈心
<lb n="0226b16"/>誦一遍即差</p><p place="inline">又法&CB00057;土二十一遍。散自身
<lb n="0226b17"/>上。一切人<note n="0226036" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">見＋（者）&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0226036"><lem>見</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">見者</rdg></app>無不敬仰。欲令自身有威光
<lb n="0226b18"/>者。&CB00057;墨塗額上。一切人見者無不愛仰。&CB00057;
<lb n="0226b19"/>灰二十一遍。塗其身大眾中一切人<note n="0226037" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">見＝者【甲】</note><app n="0226037"><lem>見</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">者</rdg></app>皆福
<lb n="0226b20"/>德相。眾人供養。欲得遠涉道路不被惡人
<lb n="0226b21"/>惡<note n="0226038" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">狩＝獸&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0226038"><lem>狩</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">獸</rdg></app>傷害。行<note n="0226039" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">加＝如&M062485;【原】</note><sic n="0226039" corr="如" resp="【原】">加</sic>奔馬。&CB00057;左<note n="0226040" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">手＋（以四指握）&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0226040"><lem>手</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">手以四指握</rdg></app>大母指作
<lb n="0226b22"/><note n="0226041" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">印＝拳&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0226041"><lem>印</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">拳</rdg></app>。而去欲得於鏡看事。&CB00057;童<note n="0226042" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">子＝男&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0226042"><lem>子</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">男</rdg></app>童女問吉
<lb n="0226b23"/>凶。其人即自下語。令道所病鬼姓名。即知
<lb n="0226b24"/>是何等之病</p><p place="inline">若被<note n="0226043" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">蠱＝蟲&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0226043"><lem>蠱</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">蟲</rdg></app>毒食者。&CB00057;所食物二
<lb n="0226b25"/>十一遍。其所為毒即吐出</p><p place="inline">若患鬼病&CB00057;五
<lb n="0226b26"/>色線。一遍一結一百八遍了。繫頭上或頂上
<lb n="0226b27"/>臂上。一切病患除差</p><p place="inline">若患心<note n="0226044" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">病＝痛&M062403;【原】＊</note><app n="0226044"><lem>病</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">痛</rdg></app>。&CB00057;石榴
<lb n="0226b28"/><note n="0226045" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔花〕－【甲】</note><app n="0226045"><lem>花</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>汁飲之即愈</p><p place="inline">若欲攝<note n="0226046" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">狐魅＝野狐&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0226046"><lem>狐魅</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">野狐</rdg></app>病。&CB00057;五色
<lb n="0226b29"/>線。令童<note n="0226047" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">子＝女&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0226047"><lem>子</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">女</rdg></app>合<note n="0226048" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔成〕&M062403;－【原】</note><app n="0226048"><lem>成</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">&lac;</rdg></app>索。一&CB00057;一結一百八遍。繫
<pb ed="T" id="T21.1248.0226c" n="0226c"/>
<lb n="0226c01"/><note n="0226049" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">項＝頸【甲】</note><app n="0226049"><lem>項</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">頸</rdg></app>下。<note n="0226050" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">復＝更&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0226050"><lem>復</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">更</rdg></app>&CB00057;楊枝打病者即立愈</p><p place="inline">若患骨
<lb n="0226c02"/>節<note n="0226051" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔楚〕&M062403;－【原】</note><app n="0226051"><lem>楚</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">&lac;</rdg></app>病。&CB00057;<note n="0226052" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">宥＝鎖鐵&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0226052"><lem>宥</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">鎖鐵</rdg></app>刀禁其病即愈</p><p place="inline">若欲護身。
<lb n="0226c03"/>&CB00057;白芥子二十一遍。若灰若水亦然。散四方
<lb n="0226c04"/>為界</p><p place="inline">若頭<app type="＊" source="0226044"><lem>病</lem><rdg resp="【原】" wit="【？】">痛</rdg></app>或身病&CB00057;蘇烏麻油二十一
<lb n="0226c05"/>遍。摩塗其身即愈</p><p place="inline">若患耳風&CB00057;蘇二十一
<lb n="0226c06"/>遍食之愈</p><p place="inline">若患眼。&CB00057;杏人油塗之立愈</p>
<lb n="0226c07"/><p>若患腫。&CB00057;石榴<note n="0226053" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">黃＝及黃檀香&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0226053"><lem>黃</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">及黃檀香</rdg></app>一百八遍塗上即愈。或白
<lb n="0226c08"/>檀香亦得</p><p place="inline">若患頭<note n="0226054" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">病＝頂&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0226054"><lem>病</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">頂</rdg></app>。&CB00057;大黃二十一遍。塗
<lb n="0226c09"/>額上即愈</p><p place="inline">若患時氣病。&CB00057;青木香末二十
<lb n="0226c10"/>一遍。和水服之立愈</p><p place="inline">若患惡瘡疥癬者。取
<lb n="0226c11"/>利蘆<note n="0226055" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">未＝末&M062403;【原】，木【甲】</note><note n="0226055" resp="CBETA" type="mod">未＝末&M062403;【原】，＝木【甲】</note><app n="0226055"><lem>未</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">末</rdg><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">木</rdg></app>和油塗上立即除愈</p><p place="inline">若患瘧病。&CB00057;
<lb n="0226c12"/>楊枝二十一遍<note n="0226056" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">令打病人＝令病人把【甲】</note><app n="0226056"><lem>令打病人</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">令病人把</rdg></app>即時除愈</p><p place="inline">若被
<lb n="0226c13"/>蝎<note n="0226057" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">螫＝赦【甲】</note><app n="0226057"><lem>螫</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">赦</rdg></app>。&CB00057;乾脯火中<note n="0226058" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">燒之熱＝熱燒&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0226058"><lem>燒之。熱</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">熱燒</rdg></app>拄其上便即除
<lb n="0226c14"/>愈</p><p place="inline">若被蛇咬。&CB00057;畢<note n="0226059" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">&CB00425;＝撥枝&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0226059"><lem>&CB00425;</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">撥枝</rdg></app>二十一遍。塗之當下
<lb n="0226c15"/>即愈</p><p place="inline">若婦人乳腫。&CB00057;油麻嚼塗上即差</p><p place="inline">若
<lb n="0226c16"/>帶下病者。&CB00057;<note n="0226060" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔丁〕&M062403;－【原】</note><app n="0226060"><lem>丁</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">&lac;</rdg></app>香水服之<note n="0226061" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔即愈〕－【甲】</note><app n="0226061"><lem>即愈</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app></p><p place="inline">若人卒
<lb n="0226c17"/>被鬼著狂言荒語。&CB00057;水<note n="0226062" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">令＝含&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0226062"><lem>令</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">含</rdg></app><note n="0226063" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">服之＝其服&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0226063"><lem>服之</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">其服</rdg></app></p><p place="inline">若患心
<lb n="0226c18"/><app type="＊" source="0226044"><lem>病</lem><rdg resp="【原】" wit="【？】">痛</rdg></app>。&CB00057;黃土塗之</p><p place="inline">若患一切鬼<note n="0226064" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">魅＋（病）&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0226064"><lem>魅</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">魅病</rdg></app>者。&CB00057;石
<lb n="0226c19"/>榴枝一百八遍。用打病者即愈</p><p place="inline">若欲得成
<lb n="0226c20"/>就三事者。當於像前作壇。壇內散種種名花。
<pb ed="T" id="T21.1248.0227a" n="0227a"/>
<lb n="0227a01"/>設種種飲食訖。取赤銅&CB04122;一枚。雄黃三兩細
<lb n="0227a02"/>擣和蜜水為丸置像前。取荷葉覆上。以手掩
<lb n="0227a03"/>之&CB00057;不息。當有相現。若&CB00195;出時取塗身上。即
<lb n="0227a04"/>成安怛陀那。若火出時。手取火焰用塗面上。
<lb n="0227a05"/>一切眾生見此人者皆大歡喜敬仰有大威
<lb n="0227a06"/>光。所出言教人皆信受恭敬隨順。若有煖氣
<lb n="0227a07"/>其人即取塗身即得無盡</p><p place="inline">又法於舍利塔前
<lb n="0227a08"/>&CB00057;牛黃。依前藥法皆得塗身一切福德盡集
<lb n="0227a09"/>其身。所在眾生見如羅闍無異</p><p place="inline">又法<note n="0227001" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">若＋（欲）&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0227001"><lem>若</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">若欲</rdg></app>知
<lb n="0227a10"/>山間有孔似阿修羅窟者。當&CB00057;白芥子和自
<lb n="0227a11"/>身血。一&CB00057;一遍打山間孔。盡一千八遍。其山
<lb n="0227a12"/>窟自開。其阿修羅女身如火然。持諸香花<note n="0227002" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">迎＝及&M062403;【原】，取【甲】</note><note n="0227002" resp="CBETA" type="mod">迎＝及&M062403;【原】，＝取【甲】</note><app n="0227002"><lem>迎</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">及</rdg><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">取</rdg></app>
<lb n="0227a13"/>&CB00057;師來。行者入此窟內。壽命一大劫身力還
<lb n="0227a14"/>如阿修羅。亦如金剛無能損者。若欲出時亦
<lb n="0227a15"/>得一切阿修羅女隨從。若不還時亦到<note n="0227003" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">火＝大【甲】</note><app n="0227003"><lem>火</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">大</rdg></app>終
<lb n="0227a16"/>無所害</p><p place="inline">又法將此像向舍利塔前。香塗地
<lb n="0227a17"/>香花散於壇內。上妙供養了。取梨木作合子。
<lb n="0227a18"/>取安膳那石為末。用秦膠水為丸。盛於合子
<lb n="0227a19"/>中置壇中。行者著新淨衣。在於像前一日不
<lb n="0227a20"/>食。誦此&CB00057;一千八遍<note n="0227004" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">了＝竟&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0227004"><lem>了</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">竟</rdg></app>。亦無勞三相現。&CB00057;
<lb n="0227a21"/>一千八遍訖<note n="0227005" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">塗＝用【甲】</note><app n="0227005"><lem>塗</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">用</rdg></app>眼竟。<note n="0227006" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">即＝亦&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0227006"><lem>即</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">亦</rdg></app>塗&CB00560;<note n="0227007" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">掌＝常【甲】</note><app n="0227007"><lem>掌</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">常</rdg></app>心中胸前
<lb n="0227a22"/>兩膊上<note n="0227008" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔頂〕&M062403;－【原】</note><app n="0227008"><lem>頂</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">&lac;</rdg></app>竟。至心合掌思身如虛空。無有
<lb n="0227a23"/>身相作<note n="0227009" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">自＝此&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0227009"><lem>自</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">此</rdg></app>想時。行者隱形日行千里。一切事
<lb n="0227a24"/>業&CB00278;皆悉見</p><p place="inline">又法欲得伏外道入火中。取自
<lb n="0227a25"/>身血魚血。瞋心誦此&CB00057;二十一遍。投火中即
<lb n="0227a26"/>入火中。<note n="0227010" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">得一頃食＝經一食頃&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0227010"><lem>得一頃食</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">經一食頃</rdg></app>間不燒其身</p><p place="inline">又法若欲
<lb n="0227a27"/>降伏外道。手中結印。瞋心誦&CB00057;一百八遍。外
<lb n="0227a28"/>道所作法悉破壞&CB00278;不成就</p><p place="inline">又法若欲降伏
<lb n="0227a29"/>諸國兵賊眾者。當畫一像身卦紫磨真金甲。
<pb ed="T" id="T21.1248.0227b" n="0227b"/>
<lb n="0227b01"/>於淨室中燒眾名香乳頭薰陸香。諸色香花
<lb n="0227b02"/>飲食供養。<note n="0227011" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">真＝瞋&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0227011"><lem>真</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">瞋</rdg></app>心誦念天王真言十萬遍。天王
<lb n="0227b03"/>領天兵來助。他國兵敵自退散。若能晝夜誦
<lb n="0227b04"/>念不絕。天王使太子獨健。領天兵千人衛護
<lb n="0227b05"/>不離其側。所求如意應念隨心。皆得成就</p>
<lb n="0227b06"/><p>又法若欲降前敵眾者。於淨室持齋畫一天
<lb n="0227b07"/>王形像。卦紫磨真金甲。於二丈竿懸。軍前五
<lb n="0227b08"/>十步指其敵。其敵不能相患</p><p place="inline">印相二小指
<lb n="0227b09"/><note n="0227012" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔相〕－【甲】</note><app n="0227012"><lem>相</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>鉤。二無名指向外直豎。二中指<note n="0227013" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔二頭指〕－【甲】</note><app n="0227013"><lem>二頭指</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>
<lb n="0227b10"/>反相叉。二大母<note n="0227014" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔指〕－【甲】</note><app n="0227014"><lem>指</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>向外直豎。手掌<note n="0227015" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">背合＝相背&M062403;【原】，〔背〕－【甲】</note><app n="0227015"><lem>背合</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">相背</rdg><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">合</rdg></app>即
<lb n="0227b11"/>是其印。如前所說一一諸法。皆用此印即得
<lb n="0227b12"/>成就。今我說根本印。以二手右押左內相
<lb n="0227b13"/>叉。豎無<note n="0227016" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">名＋（指）&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0227016"><lem>名</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">名指</rdg></app>頭相<note n="0227017" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">合＋（屈）&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0227017"><lem>合</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">合屈</rdg></app>。二頭指<note n="0227018" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔屈〕&M062403;－【原】</note><app n="0227018"><lem>屈</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">&lac;</rdg></app>如鉤。若迎
<lb n="0227b14"/>請時向身招。若<note n="0227019" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">撥＝發【甲】</note><app n="0227019"><lem>撥</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">發</rdg></app>遣時<note n="0227020" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（向）&M062403;＋外【原】</note><app n="0227020"><lem>外</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">向外</rdg></app>撥。念<note n="0227021" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">請＝誦&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0227021"><lem>請</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">誦</rdg></app>時結印
<lb n="0227b15"/>當心誦七遍。<note n="0227022" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">印＝即&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0227022"><lem>印</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">即</rdg></app>頂上散。然後取念珠專<note n="0227023" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">住＝注&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0227023"><lem>住</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">注</rdg></app>
<lb n="0227b16"/>念誦</p><p place="inline">次說吉祥天<note n="0227024" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">女＋（身）&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0227024"><lem>女</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">女身</rdg></app>印。<note n="0227025" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔以〕&M062403;－【原】</note><app n="0227025"><lem>以</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">&lac;</rdg></app>二手虛心合
<lb n="0227b17"/>掌開二頭指二中指二無名指。<note n="0227026" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔未〕&M062403;－【原】</note><app n="0227026"><lem>未</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">&lac;</rdg></app>屈如蓮華
<lb n="0227b18"/>形。二大指二小指豎合。若念<note n="0227027" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">誦＋（時）&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0227027"><lem>誦</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">誦時</rdg></app>當心結<note n="0227028" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔印〕－【甲】</note><app n="0227028"><lem>印</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>。
<lb n="0227b19"/>誦真言七遍頂上散印。四天王經云。若有人
<lb n="0227b20"/>誦念此北方毘沙門天王真言。供養&CB00025;&CB00031;飲
<lb n="0227b21"/>食。每月取一十五日二十一日。音聲用單雙
<lb n="0227b22"/>絃方響鼓舞。蘇蜜乳粥真心誦念其天王即
<lb n="0227b23"/>見其身隨心所願</p><juan fun="close" n="001"></juan></div1><div1 type="W">
<lb n="0227b24"/><p>解穢陀羅尼</p><p type="dharani">唵俱嚕馱唵&CB03928;</p><p place="inline">讚天王頌曰</p>
<lb n="0227b25"/><p>善利萬物兮惟彼水方　護持國界兮惟我
<lb n="0227b26"/>天王　良將受委兮鎮固封彊　精心奉職
<lb n="0227b27"/>兮宣託福祥　星宮上勝兮迴架崇岡　靈
<lb n="0227b28"/>像儼立兮眾寶嚴莊　威神震曜兮攝伏荒
<lb n="0227b29"/>保　又忠貞□兮<note n="0227029" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">翅＝翊&M062403;【甲】</note><app n="0227029"><lem>翅</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【甲】">翊</rdg></app>贊聖<note n="0227030" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">此次行甲本有毘沙門儀軌五字</note>唐</p>
<pb ed="T" id="T21.1248.0227c" n="0227c"/>
<lb n="0227c01"/><p><note n="0227031" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">以下甲本無之</note><note n="0227031" resp="CBETA" type="mod"><todo type="a"/>以下甲本無之</note>圓行錄云。北方毘沙門天王隨軍護法真
<lb n="0227c02"/>言一卷。不空三藏別行翻譯。八家錄亦爾
<lb n="0227c03"/>也。此法請寫於智山慈順僧正染筆。&CB01267;尾
<lb n="0227c04"/>山之本。愛染院大宣等對挍之。予亦挍閱
<lb n="0227c05"/>以上本</p>
<lb n="0227c06"/><p>　時享和辛酉八月　　長谷僧快道誌</p>
<lb n="0227c07"/><p>　一校加筆畢　　　　　　　　慈順</p>
